<page title="Installing Xuriella">

  <h3>Download</h3>
  <p>
    <strike>
      Download a
      <a href="#tbd">tarball</a>.
    </strike>
  </p>
  <p>
    Get it from git://repo.or.cz/xuriella.git
    (<a href="http://repo.or.cz/w/xuriella.git">gitweb</a>)
  </p>

  <h3>Installation</h3>
  <p>
    Xuriella needs
    <a href="http://common-lisp.net/project/cxml">cxml</a>,
    <a href="http://www.lichteblau.com/cxml-stp/">cxml-stp</a>, and
    <a href="http://common-lisp.net/project/plexippus-xpath">Plexippus XPath</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="http://www.cliki.net/asdf">ASDF</a> is used for
    compilation.  Register the .asd file, e.g. by symlinking it, then
    compile xuriella using <tt>asdf:operate</tt>.
  </p>
  <pre>$ ln -sf `pwd`/xuriella.asd /path/to/your/registry/
* (asdf:operate 'asdf:load-op :xuriella)</pre>

</page>
